        {
            "id": 6049655,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 費城半導體大漲1%，報5666.95點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間03日10:24，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲55.9點（或1%），暫報5666.95點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+2.14%</li><li>近 1 月：+16.1%</li><li>近 3 月：+29.86%</li><li>近 6 月：+11.74%</li><li>今年以來：+12.67%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)領漲。連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)上漲3.64%；英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)上漲2.42%；輝達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>)上漲2.23%；博通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AVGO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AVGO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AVGO-US</a>)上漲2.04%；美光科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>)上漲1.31%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，泰瑞達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TER:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TER\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TER-US</a>)下跌1.28%；艾司摩爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ASML:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ASML\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ASML-US</a>)下跌0.61%；英特格(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ENTG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ENTG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ENTG-US</a>)下跌0.28%；萊迪思半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LSCC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LSCC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LSCC-US</a>)下跌0.2%；芯源系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MPWR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MPWR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MPWR-US</a>)下跌0.1%。</p></section></main>",
